            <div class="col-lg-7 hidden-md hidden-sm hidden-xs homepage-copy">
                <p>We are the crew of performers, artists, musicians, magicians and Discordians who have been making waves in the UK with our production of Robert Anton Wilson’s Cosmic Trigger.</p>

                <p>For the 10th anniversary of Bob’s death, we have been instructed by signs, synchronicity, sigils and silliness to embark upon a pilgrimage to Santa Cruz and create an offering of our production. And since the mayor of Santa Cruz declared the day Bob maybe made contact with Sirius ‘Robert Anton Wilson Day’, we intend to perform this on July 23rd 2017.</p>

                <p>However, the agents of Greyface won’t fund our efforts, but the show, as we know, must go on…</p>

