                <p>We discovered recently that Horkos, the son of Eris is the keeper of the sacred oath – and we can tell you, he ain’t one to be messed with – so be sure to pledge only if you are fully committed to finding the Others, spreading the magic, and keeping the lasagna flying.</p>

                <p>We have discovered in the UK that a performance of Cosmic Trigger is like a ‘poulice of Weird’ – wherever it is applied it will draw out all the surrounding weirdness. And we gotta find that weird – we need it to have a chance of coping with the winds that are a-blowin.</p>

                <p>So please, pledge now For The Love of Bob.</p>
